{"word":"G4412 - πρῶτον - prōton - pro'-ton - Before","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρῶτον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prōton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro'-ton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Before</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முந்தின, முதலாவதான, மூத்தவனான, மூப்பரான, ஆதியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"before, at the beginning, at the first, chiefly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of <a href=\"#/G4413 - πρῶτος - prōtos - pro'-tos/4413\">G4413</a> as an adverb (with or without <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a>); <i>firstly</i> (in time, place, order, or importance): - before, at the beginning, chiefly, (at, at the) first (of all).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4409/4409\">G4409</a>, <a href=\"#/G4410/4410\">G4410</a>, <a href=\"#/G4411/4411\">G4411</a>, <a href=\"#/G4412/4412\">G4412</a>, <a href=\"#/G4413/4413\">G4413</a>, <a href=\"#/G4414/4414\">G4414</a>, <a href=\"#/G4415/4415\">G4415</a>, <a href=\"#/G4416/4416\">G4416</a>"}]}